    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ConsoleView
    Console-based implementation of the View interface.
    DetectionResult
    Represents recognition results of an image.
    FileStorageService
    Interface for storing and retrieving detection results.
    Image
    Represents an image uploaded by a user.
    ImageAnalyzerService
    Interface for analyzing images and returning detected labels.
    ImageController
    Controller that coordinates image uploads, analysis, and result retrieval.
    InMemoryFileStorageService
    In-memory implementation of FileStorageService that mimics AWS DynamoDB behavior.
    InMemoryUserRepository
    In-memory implementation of UserRepository for testing and development.
    JsonView
    JSON-based implementation of the View interface.
    Label
    Represents a label recognized from an image.
    MockRekognitionService
    A mock implementation of the ImageAnalyzerService interface.
    SwingView
    Swing-based GUI implementation of the View interface.
    SwingViewPro
    Enhanced Swing-based GUI implementation of the View interface (Pro Version).
    User
    Represents a user of the VisionTaggerApp.
    User.Type
     
    UserManagementView
    View for managing user authentication and registration in console mode.
    UserRepository
    Repository interface for managing User persistence and retrieval.
    UserService
    Service for managing user creation and validation.
    View
    Interface for rendering detection results in different formats.
    VisionTaggerApp
    Main application entry point for VisionTagger.
